Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:18.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:24.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:36.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:52.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.73,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:17.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:23.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:39.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, Misa, Max, and Kakizaki were\Ncaptured by the Zentradi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and taken to their distant main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:47.19,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their determination to\Nreturn to the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:50.31,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,gave rise to a miracle beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.59,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(99,125)}BLUE WIND
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so close now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think we'll be able to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask the Zentradi\Nfleet surrounding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the brass worry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:20.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy won't cut you any slack just\Nbecause you're the alternate watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:22.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:28.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, three micloned Zentradi spies\Nhave infiltrated the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we don't have that much\Nintel on them, but this is cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can walk\Naround looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't relax unless I'm in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:47.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit the disco!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change in the locker room over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:02:59.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Disco"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. That word wasn't in\Nour immersion training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a note of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fever! Fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have to change uniforms\Ndepending on where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warera, take note of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:20.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they changed uniforms\Nin there, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warera, aren't you ready yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:47.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having trouble getting this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:48.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. All right, now our\Nmission really begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it looked like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I recall seeing ship silhouettes\Nstretching even farther out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not counting the smaller ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we estimate there to be between\Nfour and five million of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Im... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let's hear more of what they have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:43.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, Hikaru, and the others explain that\NZentradi society is completely military,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,with no concept of civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:50.27,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, because Zentradi history\Nis one of continuous warfare,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:54.10,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,they theorize that the Zentradi used artificial\Nmeans to turn themselves into a race of giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,And that they can shrink themselves through\Na process called "micloning."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:03.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,They also describe the enemy's fear that humans\Nhave something called "Protoculture,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and relate in detail everything they\Nobserved on the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure they weren't just brainwashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:15.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, physical and mental evaluations\Nboth came back normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is this "Protoculture?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to refer to the ancestors of the giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:27.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They think that Protoculture has the power\Nto destroy their society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! That'll make it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:41.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is true, it would explain why despite their\Npower they have yet to attack the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:45.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and it would explain the inconsistency in the\Nattacks launched against the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Hayase, anything to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure remembered a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her brain's on a whole different\Nlevel from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The question now is, how do\Nwe respond to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:06:01.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get this information\Nto Earth, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send a coded message at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:03.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to try to break through\Nthe enemy blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:15.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth is two days away at maximum thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get back eventually,\Nso why not now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're the Protoculture, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You all are on shipboard leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to involve\Nyourselves in the fight so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's a welcome-back reception\Nfor you that's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}All right! I'm gonna stuff myself\Non some fine food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:50.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I believe you. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Captain Global.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get this strategy\Nmeeting underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they didn't really believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:09.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame them. I saw it with my own\Neyes and even I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had that video pack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we all got promoted, so they're\Nat least giving us some credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Leader made 1st Lieutenant, and Max\Nand I made 2nd Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be as cheerful as you, Kakizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So many amazing machines.\NAnd so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be an important section of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing like this on our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:09.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange though.\NIt just doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?! PERVERT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Males and females are interacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! But it looks like we've\Nalready passed a lot of them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their uniforms are so mixed-up\Nthat I didn't even realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this sort of thing allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:36.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how close they are to one other!\NIt... It's hideous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it may hold some significance for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Gangway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be fainting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that guy's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we seem to be attracting attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, are our uniforms not on properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem any different from\Nhow the others wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this uniform doesn't feel quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so breezy around the legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warera, it's you!\NYou're wearing a female uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better get out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Women go in that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call "culture"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this where they held the\NMiss Macross contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:31.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory works fine for\Nthings like that, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:41.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are, the four heroes who\Nmiraculously made it back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:45.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Misa Hayase, the most\Nheroic woman in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Hikaru Ichijo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the young hero who flies through the heavens\Non heavenly wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining them are Hayao Kakizaki and\NMaximilian Jenius! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, our very own Miss Macross\Nand latest singing sensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:05.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Minmay, will present them\Nall with bouquets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, who is this reception for anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... although I do like Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like these flashy\Nsorts of events either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:31.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this doesn't happen very often,\Nso where's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we both got famous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stay calm. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I'm gonna faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:17.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, in honor of our heroes,\NI'd like to sing my debut song, "My Boyfriend is a Pilot."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:28.43,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Min...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:32.94,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:35.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Happy Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.58,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them! How did they escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Protoculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:46.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, my body's starting to feel hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:52.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:59.76,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:01.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:03.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you, you love me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:13.82,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For his plane instead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, the lights are just a little bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Min...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:24.34,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Happy Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're a captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Captain Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:53.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How's it feel to be back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always\Nhave to be so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never enjoy life that way!\NJust be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ooh, wow! Is this where I work?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you want me to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:12.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes great. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:27.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, don't you have special leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I feel most comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}It's her!\N{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't come to see me at all!\NHow heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you all think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear the announcement, sir?\NWe're to report to section B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your orders were to remain on\Nthe ship on standby, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain Hayase is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! There's a difference between\Nbeing inside and outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now head back to the barracks\Nand get some sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! Or do you wanna\Ngo to the brig instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir! Going back, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Just so long as you\Nunderstand! See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross has begun to accelerate.\NRange to target increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Bodolzaa did not order its destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll follow it and observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are at maximum thrust\Nand maintaining speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any reaction from the enemy fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They've begun to match our speed and\Nare maintaining their envelopment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:16.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected. They're following,\Nbut not taking direct action.  It looks like your theory was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now passing into the Moon's orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And the enemy fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No change, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie and Ghost squadrons have\Nassembled in section B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is here and we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At full speed, their range\Nis increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:35.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This blockade of ours is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we sit by and do nothing, it will bring\Nshame to the Kamujin Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Oigur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:47.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the damned thing!\NIt's the only way I'll be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:50.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, increase speed and prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of the enemy fleet has changed course\Nand is advancing toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately ten ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy all defense forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:06.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie and Ghost squadrons,\Nlaunch all units!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie and Ghost squadrons,\Nlaunch all units!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin Transformation and activate the Pinpoint Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Civilian evacuation of all blocks is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning Transformation in all blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone vanished after that\N"transformation" announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. Very well-organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps civilians are\Npart of their military.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Why is it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be "culture," too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The artificial gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Transformation in the starboard\Nsection is 75% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation in the port section\Nis 80% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting energy-conduit system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That group from the enemy fleet\Nis headed straight at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall back! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Secondary starboard thrusters have been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,E block engineering section has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Section 27 has been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my theory is wrong, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, no second guessing yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:54.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess. Damn that Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:13.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do? Lord Bodolzaa has\Nnot ordered us to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the fleet in front of Kamujin\Nand force him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that will break\Nup our formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The main fleet is moving to join the\Ngroup already attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier won't hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:49.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin! Lord Bodolzaa has not ordered\Nthe destruction of the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As the direct commander of this fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will carry out the Supreme Commander's orders\Nuntil I am told otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:59.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Abort this unauthorized attack or you\Nwill be fighting the entire fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kamujin, I don't think she's bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:12.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why does something always\Nstop me from cutting loose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:26.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Lap'Lamiz, always flaunting her rank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume I'll let\Nthis insult pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? They shielded us\Nfrom their own attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about that later!\NWe're re-entering the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:39.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the Valkyries keeping up with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, and losses are minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Set course for UN Forces\NHigh Command in Alaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those damaged starboard thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We just lost the Number 7\Ngravity control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't maintain altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, prepare for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:04.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:05.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We're home, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}We're home!\N{\b1\c&H00FFFF&}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:22.57,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has touched down\Nin the Pacific Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:27.52,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has touched down\Nin the Pacific Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.77,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, thank you\Nfor all your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:37.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:39.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:41.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:42.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:52.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth! It's Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader, we've finally made it\Nback to Earth, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:59.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this warm sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:01.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:12.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie squadrons! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:17.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.60,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross had at last returned to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:28.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Zentradi menace now\Nthreatens both it and the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:35.02,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(74,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:35.02,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,457)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.64,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross has finally made it back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:44.62,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Captain Global, an even more\Nfearsome opponent lies in wait:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.24,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the Earth UN Government and\Nthe Military High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:53.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they accept the difficult-to-believe\Ntruth about the Zentradi threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:56.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"GLOBAL REPORT"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:24:01.94,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,128)}GLOBAL REPORT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:22.61,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:29.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:35.66,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:43.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:49.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:56.85,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.94,0:25:04.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.44,0:25:15.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
